"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"或许是吧，但是我们没必要\n扮成幼儿园小朋友啊……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"sad02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event73-09-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"美咲","body":"听好了，我们回到正题哦？\n今天，我们要决定这次在商店街举办的\n儿童节演出上该表演什么","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":15,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"event73-09-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"育美","body":"儿童节，好怀念啊~！\n育美小时候也去玩过。很开心呢！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"event73-09-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"这是商店街的人们和\n附近的幼儿园、托儿所的孩子们一起创建的\n地域性节日呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event73-09-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soun